### Example 23: Finding the Whole from a Percent

<!-- BUILD: 35% of some number is 70. What is the number? Set up 35/100 = 70/x, solve for x. -->

```scheme
(define percent 35)
(define part 70)

(define whole (exact/->float (exact// (exact/* (exact/rat part 1) (exact/rat 100 1))
                                      (exact/rat percent 1))))

(print percent \"% of some number is \" part \".\")
(print \"The whole: \" whole)
```

[VISUAL: Printed output showing the whole is 200.0]

