(define a (exact/rat 3 4))
(define b (exact/rat 2 5))
(define quotient (exact// a b))

(print (exact/->string a) \" ÷ \" (exact/->string b) \" = \" (exact/->string quotient))
```

[VISUAL: Printed output showing 3/4 ÷ 2/5 = 15/8]

Division by a fraction is multiplication by its reciprocal. `exact//` does this automatically.

