### Example 35: Rational Arithmetic Expression

<!-- BUILD: Evaluate (1/2 + 1/3) * (2/5 - 1/4). Print the result step by step. -->

```scheme
(define a (exact/rat 1 2))
(define b (exact/rat 1 3))
(define c (exact/rat 2 5))
(define d (exact/rat 1 4))

(define sum (exact/+ a b))
(define diff (exact/- c d))
(define result (exact/* sum diff))

(print \"(\" (exact/->string a) \" + \" (exact/->string b) \") = \" (exact/->string sum))
(print \"(\" (exact/->string c) \" - \" (exact/->string d) \") = \" (exact/->string diff))
(print (exact/->string sum) \" * \" (exact/->string diff) \" = \" (exact/->string result))
```

[VISUAL: Printed step-by-step showing (1/2 + 1/3) = 5/6, (2/5 - 1/4) = 3/20, result = 1/8]

