<!-- BUILD: Draw a simple probability tree as text (or describe it). Show all outcomes and their probabilities. -->

```scheme
(print \"Probability tree for two coin flips:\")
(print \"\")
(print \"       H (1/2)\")
(print \"      / \")
(print \"Start \")
(print \"      \\\\ \")
(print \"       T (1/2)\")
(print \"\")
(print \"Each branch splits again:\")
(print \"  H -> H (1/4), H -> T (1/4)\")
